room_title: Escape room "The Signal" by Hall Of Shadows Escape Games in Redlands
room_address: 320 N E St B110 San Bernardino, CA 92401
room_description: An alien craft has been detected approaching Earth and its intentions are unknown. A signal from the craft has been detected and it will be up to you and your team to take action. You must enter the abandoned communications center, lock onto the signal, and find a way to decode it. You must then determine if this ship is friend or foe and respond accordingly.
